<div class="entry-content"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-snippet wprm-recipe-template-snippet-basic-buttons"><a href="#recipe" data-recipe="16109" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path data-color="color-2" d="M9,2h6c0.6,0,1-0.4,1-1s-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,0,8,0.4,8,1S8.4,2,9,2z"></path> <path fill="#ffffff" d="M16,11V5c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,4,8,4.4,8,5v6H1.9L12,23.6L22.1,11H16z"></path></g></svg></span> Jump to Recipe</a>

<a href="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wprm_print/16109" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-print wprm-recipe-link wprm-print-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-print-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent" data-recipe-id="16109" data-template="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-print-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="16px" height="16px" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g ><path fill="#ffffff" d="M19,5.09V1c0-0.552-0.448-1-1-1H6C5.448,0,5,0.448,5,1v4.09C2.167,5.569,0,8.033,0,11v7c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h4v4c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h12c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-4h4c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-7C24,8.033,21.833,5.569,19,5.09z M7,2h10v3H7V2z M17,22H7v-9h10V22z M18,10c-0.552,0-1-0.448-1-1c0-0.552,0.448-1,1-1s1,0.448,1,1C19,9.552,18.552,10,18,10z"/></g></svg></span> Print Recipe</a></div><input class="jpibfi" type="hidden"><p>I always return to the basics and these Chicken Burritos have been in my kitchen for the past couple weeks.&nbsp;</p>
<p>You simply can't beat the flavor of&nbsp; homemade Salsa Verde -- it will turn any dish you make into a keeper!</p>
<p>So feel free to adjust the protein or fillings in these burritos, but please no skimping on the Salsa.&nbsp; It's a gamechanger 🙂</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-16099 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202560%201967'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1967" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-300x231.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1536x1180.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-2048x1574.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-150x115.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-16099 size-full" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1967" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-300x231.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1536x1180.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-2048x1574.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-150x115.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></noscript></p>
<h2>How To Make Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde</h2>
<p>I still think the best way to roast your tomatillos is to plop them in the oven -- it's easy, hands off, and efficient.</p>
<p>Here's what this batch looked like after twenty minutes in a 400F oven:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16104" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202360%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2360" height="1800" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg 2360w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-300x229.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-1024x781.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-768x586.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-1536x1172.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-2048x1562.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-150x114.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2360px) 100vw, 2360px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16104" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2360" height="1800" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven.jpg 2360w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-300x229.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-1024x781.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-768x586.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-1536x1172.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-2048x1562.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-tomatillos-after-roasting-in-oven-150x114.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2360px) 100vw, 2360px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Note that it's common to boil tomatillos, but I've tested that in the past and think the higher temp of the oven gives you superior flavor.&nbsp; <a href="https://www.mexicanplease.com/4-different-ways-make-salsa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">See this post on various ways to roast your tomatillos.</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Once you've got your tomatillos roasted, plop them in the blender with the other ingredients:</p>
<p>1/2 small onion<br />
1 garlic clove<br />
1 serrano (or less for a milder version)<br />
10-12 sprigs cilantro</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16103" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202443%202000'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2443" height="2000" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg 2443w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-300x246.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-1024x838.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-768x629.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-1536x1257.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-2048x1677.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-150x123.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2443px) 100vw, 2443px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16103" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2443" height="2000" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_.jpg 2443w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-300x246.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-1024x838.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-768x629.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-1536x1257.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-2048x1677.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/salsa-verde-ingredients-waiting-in-blender_-150x123.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2443px) 100vw, 2443px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Yes, feel free to use jalapeno if that's what you have available as it will work just as well.&nbsp;</p>
<p>And as usual, if it's been awhile since you've made Salsa Verde it's usually best to add the heat incrementally.&nbsp; Chop the serrano/jalapeno in half, or quarters, and add a sliver at a time.&nbsp; Blend, taste test, and keep adding more until the heat tastes right to you.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16102" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202287%201900'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2287" height="1900" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg 2287w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-300x249.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-1024x851.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-768x638.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-1536x1276.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-2048x1701.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-150x125.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2287px) 100vw, 2287px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16102" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2287" height="1900" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde.jpg 2287w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-300x249.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-1024x851.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-768x638.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-1536x1276.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-2048x1701.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spoonful-of-freshly-chopped-salsa-verde-150x125.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2287px) 100vw, 2287px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Have I mentioned that homemade Salsa Verde is a gamechanger?</p>
<p>It really is and I get tons of mileage from it -- please give it a go if you're new to it!</p>
<p>Once you've got the Salsa Verde on hand the rest of the ingredients are flexible.&nbsp; For this batch I coated some chicken in chile powder and cooked it off with some onion, then made a quick batch of white rice, and also chopped up a bowl of <a href="https://www.mexicanplease.com/the-only-guacamole-recipe-youll-ever-need/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Easy Guacamole</a>.&nbsp; I'll put directions for these in the recipe box below if you want to add them to your epic burritos.&nbsp;</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16098" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202560%201749'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1749" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-300x205.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-1024x699.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-768x525.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-1536x1049.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-2048x1399.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-150x102.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16098" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1749" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-300x205.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-1024x699.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-768x525.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-1536x1049.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-2048x1399.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-loaded-with-ingredients-just-before-folding-150x102.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></noscript></p>
<p>So in the above pic I'm using:</p>
<p>rice<br />
chicken<br />
Salsa Verde<br />
guacamole<br />
cheese (it's under the rice!)</p>
<p>Loaded up in a flour tortilla that's been slightly warmed so that it's easier to roll.&nbsp;</p>
<p>And please don't forget that final step of crisping up your burrito in a skillet over mediumish heat.&nbsp; This makes a huge difference as it will melt the cheese and enhance the flavor of the tortilla.&nbsp;</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16099" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202560%201967'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1967" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-300x231.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1536x1180.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-2048x1574.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-150x115.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16099" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1967" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-300x231.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1024x787.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-1536x1180.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-2048x1574.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/burrito-after-crisping-it-up-and-cut-in-half-2-150x115.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Yum!</p>
<p>And yes, you're welcome to add a spoonful of Salsa Verde to each bite if you want to.&nbsp;</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%202560%201762'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1762" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-300x206.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-1024x705.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-768x529.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-1536x1057.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-2048x1409.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-150x103.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16100" src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg" alt="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" width="2560" height="1762" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.mexicanplease.com/chicken-burritos-with-freshly-made-salsa-verde/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Chicken Burritos with Freshly Made Salsa Verde" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg" srcset="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-300x206.jpg 300w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-1024x705.jpg 1024w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-768x529.jpg 768w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-1536x1057.jpg 1536w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-2048x1409.jpg 2048w, https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/closeup-of-burrito-cut-in-half-cheesy-150x103.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></noscript></p>
<p>These are simple, easy meals to make and I always come back to them.&nbsp; Always!</p>
<p>Because when you make the Salsa Verde from scratch you'll get a massive upgrade in flavor compared to jarred Salsa.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>Enjoy 🙂</p>
