	<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-95099">
	<article id="article-comment-95099">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Boo</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">February 21, 2026 at 11:03 am</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://www.mexicanplease.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
Sometimes the simplest recipes taste the yummiest, full of flavor, because using the freshest produce brings out the deliciousness. This is the case with your wonderful recipes. Thanks for not using chicken, tomato bouillon. Use the freshest ingredients, cook with what is available during the season.<br />
Thanks for sharing with us</p>
		</div>

